By Samuel Oamen  Nollywood star, Funke Akindele Bello, has announced the death of her father, a retired school principal through her Instagram and Twitter accounts. She shared a picture of herself and her late dad and wrote: “Dad!!! May your soul Rest In Peace!! I tried Dad! I did!! We love you but God knows best!!! #iwishicanturnbackthehandsoftime” May his soul rest in peace.